div.p:
"Have they not read the scriptures which say ye must take upon you the name of Christ,
which is my name? For by this name shall ye be called at the last day—[That great day when
we shall be called to stand before him to be judged];

"And it shall come to pass, that whoso repenteth and is baptized in my name shall be filled;
and if he endureth to the end, behold, him will I hold guiltless before my Father at that day
when I shall stand to judge the world.
